org.incendo.jenkins

Class Jenkins

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.incendo.jenkins.Jenkins

  • public class Jenkins
extends Object
    Jenkins4J instance class. Instances are retrieved using a JenkinsBuilder, which can be initialized using newBuilder()
